# Dashboard Patterns (Behance 2026 trend-aligned)

## Layout (per Dammyjay93 + Leonxlnx rules)

- Sidebar: SAME bg as canvas + border-r (NOT different color — fragments space)
- Top bar: 56px height (NOT 64) — denser
- Content max-width: NO max-width on admin (data-dense)
- Spacing base: 4px (use 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32)

## Data Tables (TanStack Table v8 + shadcn)

- Server-side pagination — NEVER client-side for >100 rows
- Use `nuqs` for URL state (search, filter, page) → shareable links
- Row height: 36-40px (compact density)
- Tabular nums: `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums` on number columns
- Mono font for IDs, timestamps, amounts

## Charts (Recharts via shadcn/ui chart)

- Use shadcn `<ChartContainer>` wrapper for theme integration
- Single accent color per chart (Lila ban applies)
- Tooltip: custom with mono font + tabular nums
- Empty state: composed message, NOT empty chart skeleton

## Cards (anti-generic)

- Metric cards: each card has UNIQUE internal structure (sparkline / progress ring / delta badge)
- NOT all cards icon-left-number-big-label-small (signals AI-generated)
- For VISUAL_DENSITY > 7: NO card containers — use `divide-y` + `border-t` instead

## Command Palette (cmdk, ⌘K)

- Required for admin dashboards (power-user feature)
- Routes + entities + actions all searchable
- Recent items at top

## States (mandatory, per Leonxlnx)

- Loading: skeletal loaders matching layout (NOT spinner)
- Empty: composed "getting started" view (NOT just empty)
- Error: inline messages (NOT window.alert)
- Tactile: `-translate-y-[1px]` on `:active`

## Dark Mode (CSS vars)

- OKLCh colors (Tailwind v4 native)
- Off-black: `#0a0a0a` or `oklch(0.15 0 0)` — NOT pure `#000000`
- Higher elevation = slightly lighter bg
- Borders carry hierarchy in dark mode (shadows invisible)

## Forbidden (Leonxlnx + Dammyjay93 combined)

- ❌ Serif fonts (use Geist/Satoshi + Geist Mono/JetBrains Mono)
- ❌ Purple/blue AI gradient ("Lila ban")
- ❌ 3-column equal card rows (asymmetric/zig-zag instead)
- ❌ Generic names: John Doe, Acme Corp, SmartFlow
- ❌ Round numbers: 99.99%, 50%, $100.00 (use 47.2%, $99, +1 (312) 847-1928)
- ❌ Mixing depth strategies (borders-only OR shadows — never both)
- ❌ Different bg color for sidebar
- ❌ Lighter bg for inputs (use darker)
